  "milestone150Body": "The cortisol rollercoaster caused by blood sugar swings is a thing of the past. Your body's stress-response system is calmer and more regulated, improving your mood and resilience.",
  "milestone150Mind": "You may find you're less reactive to daily stressors. You have more emotional bandwidth.",
